{"tid":988796,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"劉小麗將提出選舉呈請","createTime":"2019-01-20T11:30:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-20T11:48:42.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3a30ce6c0510ec672a0ecf50f9c328499b5576d3","tid":988796,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T11:30:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190120/20595082\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190120%2F20595082&d=DiHeWtdYrRpCJzMVDAV9vgtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=ea3d567c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190120%2F20595082&h=10b2c8f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190120/20595082</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年01月20日 <br />\n<br />\n劉小麗將提出選舉呈請<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190120/large/19011250.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190120%2Flarge%2F19011250.jpg&h=8d3bbef6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n劉小麗將在下周限期屆滿前提出選舉呈請，挑戰選舉主任決定。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】去年11月立法會九龍西補選中，選舉主任以主張自決為由，裁定劉小麗提名無效。事隔兩個月，劉小麗向《蘋果》表示，她將在下周限期屆滿前提出選舉呈請，挑戰選舉主任決定，預料守護公義基金會負擔部份訟費，至於餘額則向市民眾籌。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n料眾籌律師費<br />\n<br />\n劉小麗指，法援和選舉呈請文件已準備妥當，在守護公義基金確認支援她的案件後，她將提出選舉呈請。但律師費龐大，小麗即使獲基金資助部份訟費，亦需向市民眾籌餘額。她稱選舉主任在無充份證據下胡亂判斷她的立場，將從選舉主任對她言論的詮釋，挑戰選舉主任DQ決定。據悉，大律師公會前主席、資深大律師石永泰會擔任劉小麗一方的代表律師。<br />\n<br />\n守護公義基金受託人鄭宇碩稱，基金已收到小麗的申請，目前尚在考慮當中，指基金成員要考慮是否有同類的案件需資助，以及基金的負擔能力，基金目前傾向支持劉小麗的申請。<br />\n<br />\n鄭宇碩透露，基金目前存款約500多萬，正支援「DQ4」原訟庭政府律師費、前議員梁國雄DQ案上訴，以及佔中九子案等，基金未來需要繼續籌款，以應付其他訴訟開支。<br />\n<br />\n■記者陳嘉裕  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n火場紅色液體流入海　貨倉爆炸「血染」大欖<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n收空郵大麻花　女生被捕"},{"pid":"7e100e9486edd55c08d6b8c56f395047d4463186","tid":988796,"uid":100697,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T11:33:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">亦需向市民眾籌餘額</span>"},{"pid":"fb47627275919acf8fd17820a00c9cac38033476","tid":988796,"uid":164590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T11:36:15.000Z","msg":"捐錢變籌旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02474d82ae51d51ba949aebbcaf4b7f5ed03d212","tid":988796,"uid":45536,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7e100e9486edd55c08d6b8c56f395047d4463186","tid":988796,"uid":100697,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T11:33:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">亦需向市民眾籌餘額</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T11:37:56.000Z","msg":"呢戰啲官司錢都叫知比左去邊 想比咪比<br />\n遊行晚會嗰啲比左佢又唔知洗左去邊就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fefb43b9f5cf23604e61ae5f449d7f0d6d9b3675","tid":988796,"uid":35730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T11:48:42.000Z","msg":"下一則<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}